@startuml
hide footbox

participant "Resource Notification Broker" as  Broker
participant "Resource Notification Recipient" as  Recipient

== Handshake Notification ==
Broker -> Recipient : [[ITI-112.html#231125-handshake-notification-request-message Handshake Notification Request Message]]
activate Recipient
Recipient --> Broker : [[ITI-112.html#231126-handshake-notification-response-message Handshake Notification Response Message]]
