== Heartbeat Notification ==
Broker -> Recipient : [[ITI-112.html#231127-heartbeat-notification-request-message Heartbeat Notification Request Message]] 
activate Recipient
Recipient --> Broker : [[ITI-112.html#231128-heartbeat-notification-response-message Heartbeat Notification Response Message]] 
deactivate Recipient

== Event Notification ==
Broker -> Recipient :  [[ITI-112.html#231129-event-notification-request-message Event Notification Request Message]]
activate Recipient
Recipient --> Broker :  [[ITI-112.html#2311210-event-notification-response-message Event Notification Response Message]]
deactivate Recipient

== Subscription Deactivation Notification ==
Broker -> Recipient :  [[ITI-112.html#2311211-subscription-deactivation-notification-request-message Subscription Deactivation Notification Request Message]]
activate Recipient
Recipient --> Broker : [[ITI-112.html#2311212-subscription-deactivation-notification-response-message Subscription Deactivation Notification Response Message]]
